(368, 7, 'home_about_about_desc', '<p class=\"about_description\">We understand the frustration and worry that come with everyday challenges like reduced mobility, managing household tasks, or caring for a loved one with dementia. These struggles can leave clients feeling isolated or families overwhelmed. That’s why our services are thoughtfully designed to provide the support needed to help clients maintain their independence and enjoy the comfort and familiarity of their own homes.</p>\r\n<p class=\"about_description\">\r\nAt Great Park Homecare, we provide personalised, compassionate care and support to help clients overcome daily challenges and live fuller, happier lives. Our English-speaking caregivers turn everyday tasks into meaningful experiences, whether it’s transforming a weekly shopping trip into a highlight of the week with a stop at a favourite café or offering companionship through shared activities like gardening.</p>\r\n'),
