(1164, 7, 'work_for_us_section_column_text_left', 'No prior experience? No problem! We provide comprehensive training and ongoing support to ensure you thrive in your role.\r\n\r\nAt Great Park Homecare, we prioritise the welfare and development of our team. Many of our staff have advanced their careers with us, achieving additional qualifications with management’s full support as they climb our career ladder.'),
