(1815, 199, 'our_impact_impact_details', '<span>Mr J</span>\r\nLiving with dementia, mornings were tough for Mr J and his wife. Great Park Homecare provides daily support with his routinae, giving Mrs J time to relax and enjoy her breakfast, allowing her to be a wife first.\r\n\r\n<span>Mrs G</span>\r\nMrs G, living alone with limited mobility and dementia, receives three daily visits for personal care, meals, medication, and errands. Weekly café outings add joy and variety to her routine.\r\n\r\n<span>Mrs B</span>\r\nWith dementia and reduced mobility, Mrs B benefits from companionship care while her daughter works. Carers engage her in gardening, music, and reminiscing, giving her daughter peace of mind.\r\n\r\n'),
