(2354, 271, 'job_section_jobs_description', 'Great Park Homecare are a high-quality care company owned and run by husband and wife team Romola & Adrian, who met whilst volunteering locally for Mencap.\r\n\r\nThey founded their home care company based on their own loved ones having sadly not experienced the high quality and trusted care they deserved or that was expected.\r\n\r\nBy understanding clients’ needs, they are able to provide much needed premium home care services as an alternative to residential care services for adults of all ages and conditions.\r\n\r\nIn fact, the company’s in-home care services are so well reputed to not only deliver peace of mind for clients and their families, but also as a local ’employer of choice’.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'),
(2355, 271, '_job_section_jobs_description', 'field_68259b239f743'),
(2356, 271, 'job_section_bottom_description', 'We’re kind and honest people to work with. We’re not like any other care provider or care staffing agency. Investing in staff qualifications, healthcare and careers, the company has created a culture of respect and camaraderie amongst like-minded outstanding home carers who are all compassionate and caring people.\r\n\r\n'),
