(2496, 278, 'job_section_bottom_description1', 'We’re kind and honest people to work with. We’re not like any other care provider or care staffing agency. Investing in staff qualifications, healthcare and careers, the company has created a culture of respect and camaraderie amongst like-minded outstanding home carers who are all compassionate and caring people.\r\n\r\n'),
